Package fakestore.model

package fakestore.model
This package contains the model classes of the FakeStore.

It defines the data structures and the logic of the application. These data structures are passed to the view through the controller to be displayed. They are also only modified by the controller and the passed down structures are either immutable or copies or their exposed public interfaces do not allow write access.
